{"hadithnumber": "110", "text": "“The Prophet (Allah bless him and give him peace) entered Mecca on the Day of Victory wearing a black turban.”"}
{"hadithnumber": "111", "text": "I saw a black turban on the head of Allah’s Messenger (Allah bless him and give him peace).”"}
{"hadithnumber": "112", "text": "The Prophet (Allah bless him and give him peace) addressed the people while wearing a black turban.”"}
{"hadithnumber": "113", "text": "When the Prophet (Allah bless him and give him peace) donned a turban, he let his turban hang down between his shoulders.”"}
{"hadithnumber": "114", "text": "“The Prophet (Allah bless him and give him peace) addressed the people while wearing a turban that was dasma’ ."}
